wf-bluespace-quirk-messages-name = bluespace quirk messages

wf-bluespace-quirk-message-1 = You feel a faint hum, like distant whispering, coming from inside.
wf-bluespace-quirk-message-2 = For a heartbeat, you swear something inside the bluespace object breathed.
wf-bluespace-quirk-message-3 = A cold draft seeps out of the opening, smelling faintly of ozone.
wf-bluespace-quirk-message-4 = You hear a soft tapping... from the inside.
wf-bluespace-quirk-message-5 = The bluespace object is heavier than it should be, just for a moment.
wf-bluespace-quirk-message-6 = Something shifts inside, even though you haven't moved.
wf-bluespace-quirk-message-7 = You catch a glimpse of stars where the bottom should be.
wf-bluespace-quirk-message-8 = A voice, far away and not your own, mutters something you can't quite make out.
